{
  "stem": "22174.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, antisemitism was rampant always in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not only in Germany, but in-- was very widespread in Europe, Western and Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Eastern Europe, it was worse, worse yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] our customers were mostly working class people and, and left-wing, organized, unionized, and organized unions and, and belonging to left-wing parties.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were not antisemitic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Antisemitism was mainly in the middle classes, middle and upper classes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] of course, in the-- in the business circles of the town, there were a few Jewish people that had businesses.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they were-- of course, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was always comp-- anyway, businesses, competition anyway.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, but most of those small storekeepers, shopkeepers, were, were right-wing people, you know, right-wing lawyers and-- and [PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] what was your question?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you have other experiences with antisemitism yourself?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] One time, I was in, in some kind of a rally in a, in a-- in the center of the town, in a marketplace.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know-- I don't remember what it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody came up to me and started-- wanted to hit me in the face.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And though there was another man, another guy, older than I-- not a student.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were all sorts of people there, and I didn't know the guy who wanted to hit me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and he, the other-- the other fellow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] prevented it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He held him back, and he was-- he was an SR, SR man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, is from, from the Nazi Stormtroopers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he held him back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I never knew why.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were kind of respected by people there, in spite of being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
